<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Pago fallido</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bad:#dc2626;
      --ink:#111827;
      --sub:#6b7280;
      --bg:#f9fafb;
      --card:#ffffff;
    }
    body {
      margin:0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial;
      background:var(--bg);
      color:var(--ink);
    }
    .wrap {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 4rem auto;
      background:var(--card);
      padding:2rem;
      border-radius:12px;
      box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
    }
    .badge {
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:.5rem;
      font-weight:600;
      color:var(--bad);
    }
    .badge svg {
      width:22px;
      height:22px;
    }
    .muted { color:var(--sub); }
    .row { margin:1rem 0; }
    .btns {
      display:flex;
      gap:.75rem;
      margin-top:1.25rem;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }
    .btn {
      padding:.75rem 1rem;
      border-radius:10px;
      text-decoration:none;
      font-weight:600;
      border:1px solid #e5e7eb;
      background:#fff;
    }
    .btn.primary {
      background:#ea580c;
      color:#fff;
      border-color:#ea580c;
    }
    code {
      background:#f3f4f6;
      padding:.25rem .5rem;
      border-radius:6px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="badge">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
        <path d="M12 9v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
              stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
      El pago no se pudo completar
    </div>

    <h1>Intenta nuevamente</h1>
    <p class="muted">Puede deberse a fondos insuficientes, datos inv√°lidos o un problema temporal con el emisor.</p>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="muted">ID de checkout</div>
      <div><code><%= params[:checkoutId] %></code></div>
    </div>

    <% if params[:error] %>
      <p class="muted"><strong>Error:</strong> <%= params[:error] %></p>
    <% end %>

    <div class="btns">
      <a class="btn primary" href="/">Volver al pago</a>
      <a class="btn" href="mailto:soporte@recurrente.com?subject=Ayuda%20con%20pago%20<%= params[:checkoutId] %>">Contactar soporte</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
